<h2>FORMAL DEMAND FOR PAYMENT OF RENT ARREARS</h2>

<p>Dear {{tenant_full_name}},</p>

<h3>Re: Property at {{property_address}}</h3>

<p>
I am writing to you about the money you owe me in respect of rent and other sums relating to the above property.
</p>

<p>
<strong>This is a final demand for payment before I raise court proceedings against you.</strong> You should read this letter carefully and seek advice if you are unsure what to do.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>1. Summary of What You Owe</h2>

