</ol>

<hr>

<h2>9. Your Rights</h2>

<p>You have the right to:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Seek free debt advice from the organisations listed above;</li>
  <li>Dispute the debt if you believe it is wrong (you must provide evidence);</li>
  <li>Request a breakdown of the arrears if the schedule is unclear;</li>
  <li>Propose a payment plan if you cannot pay in full;</li>
  <li>Defend any court proceedings if you have a valid legal defence.</li>
</ul>

<p>
<strong>However, ignoring this letter will not make the problem go away.</strong> I urge you to take action within 14 days to avoid court proceedings.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>10. Next Steps</h2>

<p>
To summarise, you must <strong>within 14 days</strong> (by {{response_deadline}}):
</p>

<ol>
  <li>Pay the full amount owed ({{currency total_claim_amount}}); OR</li>
  <li>Contact me to arrange a payment plan; OR</li>
  <li>Provide a written explanation if you dispute the debt.</li>
</ol>

<p>
If you do not respond or make payment, I will raise Simple Procedure proceedings without further notice.
</p>

